            <p>On the other hand, you can’t forget about the fantastic, spacious private suits because they are enclosed or semi-enclosed for more privacy and have doors or curtains. Luxury seating is the primary feature of business class travel, with ergonomic seats that can be easily converted into fully flat beds with plush bedding. People can also use mood lighting by adjusting lighting to create a relaxing atmosphere. </p>
            <h2>In-Flight Dining</h2>
            <p>Gourmet meals, such as multi-course meals specially prepared by the leading chefs, are only available when pre-ordering the food. The best thing about business class travel for people is the pleasing dining presentation because all the food is served in fine China with silverware and crystal glasses. You can also eat exclusive beverages such as Premium champagne, wines, cocktails, and specialty coffees or teas. On the other hand, you can also choose the flexible dining options and eat when you want with your flexible schedule. </p>
